---
title: Sweet Soy Tofu, Chicken & Katsu Curry with Garlic Rice & Garlic Greens
description: Tofu must be one of the most versatile proteins, you can flavour it however you like! Take this one for example - flavoured with sweet soy seasoning and perfectly paired with a katsu curry sauce. All you need is chicken and some garlic rice to soak up and enhance all those layers of yumminess!
